text-[#0B1F3A]\">IEC Digital Portal</span><span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Independent Elections Commission · ALSI 2026</span></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-1 md:flex\"><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/register/candidate\">Candidate Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/register/voters\">Voter Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/register/party\">Party Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/status\">Check Status</a></nav><button class=\"flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-slate-200 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-slate-700\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-slate-50\"><section class=\"border-b border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#0B1F3A]\">IEC Registration Portal</p><h1 class=\"mt-5 text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A]\">Election Registration Center</h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Official digital registration gateway for candidates, voters, and political parties participating in the 2026 ALSI General Election supervised by the Independent Elections Commission (IEC).</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/status\">Check Application Status</a><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/\">Return Home</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A]\">Registration Modules</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">Select the appropriate registration category below to begin your official IEC election application process.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"group flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full border px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide border-green-200 bg-green-50 text-green-700\">Open</div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Candidate Registration</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Submit official candidacy applications for elective positions in the 2026 ALSI General Election.</p></div><a class=\"mt-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/candidate\">Continue Registration</a></div><div class=\"group flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full border px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide border-green-200 bg-green-50 text-green-700\">Open</div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Voter Registration</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Verify voter eligibility and register for participation in the 2026 ALSI General Election.</p></div><a class=\"mt-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/voter\">Continue Registration</a></div><div class=\"group flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full border px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide border-green-200 bg-green-50 text-green-700\">Open</div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Political Party Registration</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Register political parties, upload constitutions, and submit official party documentation for IEC approval.</p></div><a class=\"mt-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/party\">Continue Registration</a></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-10 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#0B1F3A]\">Official IEC Notice</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A]\">Registration Compliance &amp; Verification Policy</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">All election applications are subject to IEC verification, document review, and compliance screening before approval.</p></div><div class=\"mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#0B1F3A]\">Document Requirements</h3><ul class=\"mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\"><li>• PDF format only</li><li>• Maximum upload size: 2MB per document</li><li>• Blurry or incomplete documents may result in rejection</li><li>• Duplicate submissions are prohibited</li><li>• Fraudulent submissions may lead to permanent disqualification</li></ul></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#0B1F3A]\">IEC Verification Workflow</h3><ul class=\"mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\"><li>• Submission received</li><li>• IEC compliance review</li><li>• Eligibility validation</li><li>• Approval or correction request</li><li>• Final election clearance</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-amber-800\">IEC reserves the right to request additional verification documents or reject submissions that do not satisfy electoral requirements and compliance regulations.</p></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><p>© 2026 Independent Elections Commission (IEC) — ALSI</p><p>Official Election Registration Platform</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03tfhzrunrhlw.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7988,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.